config_version=5

[application]

config/name="TicTacToe"
config/description="Project Overview:
This project is a digital implementation of the classic Tic-Tac-Toe game, enhanced with an AI opponent using the minimax algorithm. The goal is to create a game that provides a challenging and engaging experience through an intelligent and unbeatable computer opponent.

Features:

Classic Tic-Tac-Toe Gameplay:

A 3x3 grid where two players take turns marking spaces with X and O.
The objective is to get three of your marks in a row, column, or diagonal.
Minimax Algorithm for AI:

The AI uses the minimax algorithm to evaluate all possible moves.
It ensures optimal play by minimizing the possible loss in a worst-case scenario.
The AI will either win or draw, providing a challenging opponent for players.
User Interface:

Clean and simple design for easy interaction.
Visual indicators for player turns and game status (win, lose, draw)."
run/main_scene="res://Scenes/main.tscn"
